    "The result of this polynomial fit is a contiguously estimated α per source that is used to remove the overall PSF leakage into the source ellipticities:ε = ε -α ε PSF.",
    "(26)In practice ε is an intermediate product because, as mentioned previously, the ellipticities after this correction still contain residual biases due to higher-order bin-wise fluctuations in the distribution of α.",
